--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
INFORMATION
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This file lists changes made to the Ansible role. It follows semantic versioning
guidelines. The content is sorted in reverse chronological order and formatted
to allow easy grepping by scripts.

The fields are:
B: bug
C: change
E: enhancement
F: feature

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

* Version 3.1.0 (2020-12-31)
C: Add support for FreeBSD 12.2-RELEASE
C: Drop support for FreeBSD 12.1-RELEASE

* Version 3.0.1 (2020-10-30)
E: Simplify Ansible file header (ansible_managed)

* Version 3.0.0 (2019-11-08)
C: Rename role from 'periodic' to 'freebsd_periodic'
C: Add support for FreeBSD 12.1-RELEASE
C: Drop support for FreeBSD 12.0-RELEASE

* Version 2.5.0 (2019-05-26)
F: Port role to Ansible 2.8

* Version 2.4.0 (2019-01-13)
C: Add support for FreeBSD 12.0-RELEASE
C: Drop support for FreeBSD 11.2-RELEASE

* Version 2.3.1 (2018-10-20)
E: Update support information of OpenBSD

* Version 2.3.0 (2018-07-01)
C: Add support for FreeBSD 11.2-RELEASE
C: Drop support for FreeBSD 11.1-RELEASE

* Version 2.2.0 (2018-05-22)
F: Port role to Ansible 2.5

* Version 2.1.2 (2018-04-24)
E: Simplify role by removing 'template' option

* Version 2.1.1 (2018-04-04)
E: Update support information of OpenBSD

* Version 2.1.0 (2018-03-30)
F: Port role to Ansible 2.4

* Version 2.0.0 (2018-02-20)
E: Simplify and improve Ansible role

* Version 1.1.1 (2017-10-18)
E: Update support information of OpenBSD

* Version 1.1.0 (2017-08-26)
C: Add support for FreeBSD 11.1-RELEASE
C: Drop support for FreeBSD 11.0-RELEASE

* Version 1.0.0 (2017-08-01)
E: Stabilize, improve and cleanup Ansible role

* Version 0.5.1 (2017-04-16)
E: Update support information of OpenBSD

* Version 0.5.0 (2016-10-14)
C: Add support for FreeBSD 11.0-RELEASE
C: Drop support for FreeBSD 10.3-RELEASE

* Version 0.4.2 (2016-09-03)
E: Update support information of OpenBSD

* Version 0.4.1 (2016-05-29)
E: Improve FreeBSD support

* Version 0.4.0 (2016-05-21)
C: Add support for Ansible 2.0

* Version 0.3.0 (2016-04-09)
C: Add support for FreeBSD 10.3-RELEASE
C: Drop support for FreeBSD 10.2-RELEASE

* Version 0.2.1 (2016-04-02)
E: Update support information for OpenBSD 5.9

* Version 0.2.0 (2016-01-21)
C: Drop support for OS family 'Gentoo'

* Version 0.1.1 (2015-11-17)
E: Add missing Ansible tags

* Version 0.1.0 (2015-03-12)
F: Initial release
